# Optional: API base URL (no trailing slash).
# - Local: leave unset. Vite proxies /api to http://localhost:5000 (see vite.config.ts).
# - Production (Vercel) with backend on another host (e.g. Railway, Render):
#   Set in Vercel: Settings → Environment Variables → VITE_API_URL = https://your-backend.example.com
# - Production with same-origin API (e.g. Vercel rewrites to serverless backend): leave unset.
# VITE_API_URL=
